    name VARCHAR(50),
    email VARCHAR(50),
    phone VARCHAR(15)
);

CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    order_date TIMESTAMP,
    total_amount DECIMAL(10,2)
);

CREATE TABLE products (
    product_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(100),
    category VARCHAR(50),
    price DECIMAL(10,2)
);

CREATE TABLE marketing_messages (
    message_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    message_text TEXT,
    send_date TIMESTAMP
);
